item.description:
@kid2kewl2 wrote:

[quote=“Tony da best, post:3, topic:295082”]K, To make it say you dont need jdk or that stuff you simply… "Right click edit on the compiler and then u change the number to your jdk version like this "

@echo off
cd …
"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_13\bin
pause

the number were it says jdk1.6.0_13" u edit it with your jdk version then you save

And you have to edit the files if you want to make your self owner on a 317 you can go to the char files and open your name in word pad and were it says “Player right’s = replace the 0 with a 3” While your logged off then when you log in your the owner.[/quote]
Most likely you will only have to change the 13 to what would now be 16 i believe. (update 16)
